Система дифференциальных уравнений¶

:

\begin{matrix} \dot{x_1} &=& (u - \frac{2}{3})x_1 + \frac{x_2}{6}, \\ \dot{x_2} &=& \frac{2x_1}{3} - \frac{x_2}{6} \\ \dot{p_1} &=& - p_1 u + \frac{2}{3}(p_1 - p_2) \\ \dot{p_2} &=& - \frac{1}{6}(p_1 - p_2) \\ \end{matrix}

C : $$p_1(T) u(T)x_1(T) + \frac{1}{6}(x_2(T)-4x_1(T))(p_1(T) - p_2(T)) \ge 0$$

u : $$u = (1)I\{ x_1 p_1 > 0 \} + (-1) I\{ x_1 p_1 < 0 \} + (\forall u) I\{ x_1 p_1 = 0 \}$$

boundary_conditions = [[[3, 5], [2, 2.5]], [[0.1, 5], [1, 1.5]], [[0.01, 7.0], [2.0, 3.0]], [[4, 7], [3, 3.5]]]

#   :
def u(x1, p1):
        if (x1*p1 >= 0):
            return 1
        else:
            return -1

def f(t, y):
    x1, x2, p1, p2 = y
    u_ = u(x1, p1)
    #print(y, u_)
    
    xx1 = (u_ - 2/3)*x1 + x2/6
    xx2 = 2/3*x1 - x2/6
    pp1 = -p1*u_ + 2/3*(p1 - p2)
    pp2 = -1/6*(p1 - p2)
    return np.array([xx1, xx2, pp1, pp2])

def pipesearch(i, cur_range = np.arange(-0.5, -0.4, 0.00005)):
    #,     ,    (-2, 2), 
    #         
    
    X = rahmodule.initial_search(boundary_conditions=boundary_conditions[i], cur_range=cur_range, T_steps=400)
    p10 = cur_range[np.argmin(X[0])]
    print(f"Initial p10: {p10}")
    p20 = -1
    ans = rahmodule.idiot_optimizer(rahmodule.LOSS, [p10], others=[boundary_conditions[i]], silent=1, steps=100)
    print(f"Optimized p10: {ans[0]}")
    rahmodule.checksol(p10=ans[0], p20=-1, boundary_conditions=boundary_conditions[i], save = f"bc{i}.txt")
